      "content": "it just feels like a lot of work for nothing. like, why endure the exhaustion and the pain and the fear just to delay a certainty? if the end is coming regardless, isn't there a certain kind of relief in just... accepting it? instead of performing this constant, tiring act of \"fighting\" for nothing?",
